Uses of Package
ch.njol.skript.classes

  • Packages that use ch.njol.skript.classes 
    Package Description
    ch.njol.skript.classes
    Code related to handling the different types of Java, Skript, and Bukkit.
    ch.njol.skript.classes.data
    Contains definitions and other data of all types supported by Skript by default.
    ch.njol.skript.command
    Code related to handling commands, either Skript commands or custom script commands.
    ch.njol.skript.config
    Code for loading & saving Skript's custom configuration files (actual configs & scripts).
    ch.njol.skript.config.validate  
    ch.njol.skript.entity
    Contains definitions of Minecraft's various entity types.
    ch.njol.skript.expressions
    Contains the default expression of Skript.
    ch.njol.skript.expressions.base  
    ch.njol.skript.hooks.chat.expressions  
    ch.njol.skript.hooks.economy.expressions  
    ch.njol.skript.lang
    Contains all code related to parsing scripts.
    ch.njol.skript.lang.function  
    ch.njol.skript.lang.util  
    ch.njol.skript.registrations
    Contains classes used for registering new stuff to Skript.
    ch.njol.skript.util
    Various utility classes and methods.
